languages.text: "Ты смеешь мне перечить? Радуйся, что я не вышвырнул{mf||а} тебя в шлюз за этот провал!"
"You dare protest against my will? You should count yourself fortunate I have not yet had you thrown you out of an airlock for this blunder!"

languages.text: «¿Osa protestar contra mi voluntad? ¡Tiene suerte de que aún no la haya mandado expulsar al vacío por esto!».
languages.original_text: "You dare protest against my will? You should count yourself fortunate I have not yet had you thrown you out of an airlock for this blunder!"

traits.locale_text: «¿Osa protestar contra mi voluntad? ¡Tiene suerte de que aún no la haya mandado expulsar al vacío por esto!».

languages.text: 「我が意に背くのか？この不始末について、まだエアロックから放り出されずに済んでいることを幸運に思うんだな！」
languages.original_text: "You dare protest against my will? You should count yourself fortunate I have not yet had you thrown you out of an airlock for this blunder!"

traits.locale_text: 「我が意に背くのか？この不始末について、まだエアロックから放り出されずに済んでいることを幸運に思うんだな！」

languages.text: “你好大的胆子，竟敢反对我的命令？我没因为这个错误把你扔出气闸，你就该感恩戴德了！”
languages.original_text: "You dare protest against my will? You should count yourself fortunate I have not yet had you thrown you out of an airlock for this blunder!"

traits.locale_text: “你好大的胆子，竟敢反对我的命令？我没因为这个错误把你扔出气闸，你就该感恩戴德了！”

languages.text: "Ihr wagt es, gegen meinen Willen aufzubegehren? Ihr solltet Euch glücklich schätzen, dass ich Euch für diese Fehlleistung nicht aus einer Luftschleuse habe werfen lassen!"
languages.original_text: "You dare protest against my will? You should count yourself fortunate I have not yet had you thrown you out of an airlock for this blunder!"

languages.text: « Vous osez vous opposer à ma volonté ? Vous devriez vous estimer heureux que je ne vous aie pas encore fait expulser du vaisseau pour cette bévue ! »
